content:
this weekend is very bad ,  although i like badmition very much ,bu I didn't feel better cause i can't win .
besides , i also feel bad because i give up the opportunity  to practice singing for that i think i am not good at it
i feel lonely , i keep opening  my instagram info to see what is new.  and when i feel bad when few give a like to my reel .
我持续拖延而不是去完成的工作内容，因为我觉得太难了，我是在做调研工作，需要看很多文章，但是并没有相关经验，不知道怎么样才能做好，害怕达不到领导的要求，但是领导自己可能也不是很懂
last day night ,i do nothing but just lying bed watching tiktoks , i have been like this for many days ,i cant't help to waste my time and energy .
in this morning , i get up at 10 ,and i keep watching until 12,i just feel like i lose control of myself ,and can't be able to return my work,
in 12:20 ,my friend ask me to go to ktv ,i agree without thinking , for i lose control of  myself ,i know it is not beneficial to stay here
